query:
INSERT INTO modules (name, version, manifest, installed_at, updated_at)
            VALUES (?1, ?2, ?3, ?4, ?5)
            ON CONFLICT(name) DO UPDATE SET
                version = excluded.version,
                manifest = excluded.manifest,
                updated_at = excluded.updated_at
            RETURNING 
                name as "name!: String",
                version as "version!: String",
                manifest as "manifest!: String",
                installed_at as "installed_at!: NaiveDateTime",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: NaiveDateTime"
